{
  "info": {
    "name": "WelfareWatch — AI Anomaly Engine",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the WelfareWatch AI Anomaly Classification Engine.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}`  \n**Auth:** All `/api/anomaly/*` routes require the `X-Engine-Secret` header.\n\n---\n\n### Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman.\n2. Create an environment with the variables below.\n3. Run **Health Check** first to confirm the server and DB are up.\n\n### Environment Variables\n| Variable | Example Value |\n|---|---|\n| `base_url` | `http://localhost:3000` |\n| `engine_secret` | *(value of ENGINE_SECRET in your .env)* |\n| `anomaly_id` | `aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000001` |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",      "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "engine_secret", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "anomaly_id",    "value": "aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000001", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Returns server and DB health status. No authentication required.\n\n**Expected 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-07T09:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"services\": {\n    \"database\": \"ok\",\n    \"openai\": \"configured\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**503** is returned when the DB is unreachable."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Healthy",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-07T09:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"services\": {\n    \"database\": \"ok\",\n    \"openai\": \"configured\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "503 Degraded",
              "status": "Service Unavailable",
              "code": 503,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"degraded\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-07T09:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"services\": {\n    \"database\": \"error\",\n    \"openai\": \"configured\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Classify",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Classify Single — NO_SPIKE (CRITICAL)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",    "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Engine-Secret", "value": "{{engine_secret}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/anomaly/classify",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "anomaly", "classify"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"bbbbbbbb-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n  \"date\": \"2026-03-07\",\n  \"detector_type\": \"NO_SPIKE\",\n  \"level\": \"PINCODE\",\n  \"pincode\": \"605001\",\n  \"block\": \"Vikravandi\",\n  \"district\": \"Villupuram\",\n  \"state\": \"Tamil Nadu\",\n  \"scheme_id\": \"PDS\",\n  \"severity\": \"CRITICAL\",\n  \"score\": 4.8,\n  \"no_pct\": 0.81,\n  \"baseline_no_pct\": 0.29,\n  \"total_responses\": 158,\n  \"affected_beneficiaries\": 210,\n  \"raw_data\": {\n    \"z_score\": 4.8,\n    \"today_no_pct\": 0.81,\n    \"baseline_no_pct\": 0.29,\n    \"std_dev\": 0.109,\n    \"window\": \"2026-03-07#14\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Classifies a single anomaly record using OpenAI and writes the result back to `anomaly_records` in the database.\n\n**Auth:** `X-Engine-Secret` header required.\n\n**Body fields:**\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `id` | UUID string | ✅ | Must exist in `anomaly_records` |\n| `date` | YYYY-MM-DD | ✅ | Anomaly date |\n| `detector_type` | enum | ✅ | `NO_SPIKE` \\| `SILENCE` \\| `DUPLICATE_BENEFICIARY` \\| `DISTRICT_ROLLUP` |\n| `level` | enum | ✅ | `PINCODE` \\| `BLOCK` \\| `DISTRICT` |\n| `pincode` | 6-digit string | ✅ if PINCODE | - |\n| `block` | string | ✅ if not DISTRICT | - |\n| `district` | string | ✅ | - |\n| `state` | string | - | - |\n| `scheme_id` | enum | ✅ | `PDS` \\| `PM_KISAN` \\| `OLD_AGE_PENSION` \\| `LPG` |\n| `severity` | enum | ✅ | `CRITICAL` \\| `HIGH` \\| `MEDIUM` \\| `LOW` |\n| `score` | number | - | z-score or ratio |\n| `no_pct` | 0.0–1.0 | - | Today's NO% |\n| `baseline_no_pct` | 0.0–1.0 | - | 7-day mean NO% |\n| `total_responses` | integer | - | |\n| `affected_beneficiaries` | integer | - | |\n| `raw_data` | object | - | Full detector output |"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Classified",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"anomaly_id\": \"bbbbbbbb-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"ai_classification\": \"SUPPLY_FAILURE\",\n    \"ai_confidence\": 0.91,\n    \"ai_reasoning\": \"NO% spiked to 81% vs 7-day baseline of 29% — z-score 4.8 indicates a non-random event. Pattern consistent with FPS distribution point not opening.\",\n    \"ai_action\": \"Conduct immediate field visit to FPS store at 605001. Verify stock availability and dealer attendance.\",\n    \"ai_action_ta\": \"605001 இல் உள்ள FPS கடைக்கு உடனடி கள வருகை மேற்கொள்ளவும். பங்கு கிடைக்கும் தன்மையை சரிபார்க்கவும்.\",\n    \"ai_urgency\": \"TODAY\",\n    \"signals_used\": [\"z_score_4.8\", \"no_pct_0.81\", \"distribution_window_active\"],\n    \"confidence_adjustments\": [\n      { \"factor\": \"high_sample_size\", \"delta\": 0.05 },\n      { \"factor\": \"score_exceeds_2x_threshold\", \"delta\": 0.05 }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"model\": \"gpt-4o-mini\",\n    \"total_tokens\": 1015,\n    \"latency_ms\": 1842,\n    \"cost_usd\": 0.00024\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "500 OpenAI or DB error",
              "status": "Internal Server Error",
              "code": 500,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"anomaly_id\": \"bbbbbbbb-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n  \"error\": \"OpenAI API error: insufficient_quota\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
