              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"bbbbbbbb-0000-0000-0000-000000000004\",\n  \"date\": \"2026-03-07\",\n  \"detector_type\": \"DUPLICATE_BENEFICIARY\",\n  \"level\": \"PINCODE\",\n  \"pincode\": \"605004\",\n  \"block\": \"Vikravandi\",\n  \"district\": \"Villupuram\",\n  \"state\": \"Tamil Nadu\",\n  \"scheme_id\": \"PM_KISAN\",\n  \"severity\": \"MEDIUM\",\n  \"score\": 4,\n  \"no_pct\": null,\n  \"baseline_no_pct\": null,\n  \"total_responses\": 4,\n  \"affected_beneficiaries\": 1,\n  \"raw_data\": {\n    \"duplicate_count\": 4,\n    \"phone_hash\": \"hash_pmk_005\",\n    \"response_times\": [\"10:01\", \"11:30\", \"13:45\", \"15:20\"]\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Tests the DUPLICATE_BENEFICIARY detector type — same phone_hash responded 4 times in one day."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Batch",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Classify Batch — 2 anomalies",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",    "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Engine-Secret", "value": "{{engine_secret}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/anomaly/classify/batch",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "anomaly", "classify", "batch"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"anomalies\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cccccccc-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-03-07\",\n      \"detector_type\": \"NO_SPIKE\",\n      \"level\": \"PINCODE\",\n      \"pincode\": \"603001\",\n      \"block\": \"Madurantakam\",\n      \"district\": \"Chengalpattu\",\n      \"state\": \"Tamil Nadu\",\n      \"scheme_id\": \"PDS\",\n      \"severity\": \"HIGH\",\n      \"score\": 2.3,\n      \"no_pct\": 0.54,\n      \"baseline_no_pct\": 0.27,\n      \"total_responses\": 62,\n      \"affected_beneficiaries\": 150,\n      \"raw_data\": { \"z_score\": 2.3, \"std_dev\": 0.117 }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cccccccc-0000-0000-0000-000000000002\",\n      \"date\": \"2026-03-07\",\n      \"detector_type\": \"SILENCE\",\n      \"level\": \"BLOCK\",\n      \"pincode\": null,\n      \"block\": \"Gingee\",\n      \"district\": \"Villupuram\",\n      \"state\": \"Tamil Nadu\",\n      \"scheme_id\": \"LPG\",\n      \"severity\": \"MEDIUM\",\n      \"score\": 0.52,\n      \"no_pct\": null,\n      \"baseline_no_pct\": null,\n      \"total_responses\": 14,\n      \"affected_beneficiaries\": 230,\n      \"raw_data\": {\n        \"expected_responses\": 46,\n        \"actual_responses\": 14,\n        \"silence_ratio\": 0.696\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Classifies multiple anomaly records in one request (sequential, to respect OpenAI rate limits). Max batch size is controlled by the `BATCH_SIZE` env var (default: 5).\n\n**Body:** `{ \"anomalies\": [ ...anomaly objects... ] }`\n\n**Limits:**\n- Minimum: 1 record\n- Maximum: `BATCH_SIZE` (default 5)\n- Requests are processed sequentially with 200ms delays between calls"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Batch result",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total\": 2,\n    \"succeeded\": 2,\n    \"failed\": 0\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"success\": true,\n      \"anomaly_id\": \"cccccccc-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n      \"result\": { \"ai_classification\": \"SUPPLY_FAILURE\", \"ai_confidence\": 0.78 }\n    },\n    {\n      \"success\": true,\n      \"anomaly_id\": \"cccccccc-0000-0000-0000-000000000002\",\n      \"result\": { \"ai_classification\": \"DATA_ARTIFACT\", \"ai_confidence\": 0.61 }\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Classify Pending — from DB",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Engine-Secret", "value": "{{engine_secret}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/anomaly/classify/pending?limit=5",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "anomaly", "classify", "pending"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "5",
                  "description": "Max records to pull from DB. Defaults to BATCH_SIZE env var."
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Queries `anomaly_records` for all rows where `ai_classification IS NULL OR ai_classification = 'PENDING'`, ordered by severity (CRITICAL first), then classifies them.\n\nThis is the main **automated pipeline trigger** — call this on a schedule (e.g. every 5 minutes) to keep all anomalies classified.\n\n**Query params:**\n| Param | Default | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `limit` | `BATCH_SIZE` env var | Max records to process per call |"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 No pending",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"No pending anomalies found\",\n  \"summary\": { \"total\": 0, \"succeeded\": 0, \"failed\": 0 },\n  \"results\": []\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 Processed",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"summary\": { \"total\": 3, \"succeeded\": 3, \"failed\": 0 },\n  \"results\": [...]\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Results & Stats",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Anomaly Result by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Engine-Secret", "value": "{{engine_secret}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/anomaly/{{anomaly_id}}/result",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "anomaly", "{{anomaly_id}}", "result"]
            },
            "description": "Fetches the AI classification result for a single anomaly record from the database.\n\n**Path param:** `:id` — UUID of the anomaly record\n\nSet the `anomaly_id` collection variable to one of the seeded UUIDs:\n- `aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000001` (PDS NO_SPIKE CRITICAL — Villupuram)\n- `aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000002` (OLD_AGE_PENSION SILENCE — Chengalpattu)\n- `aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000003` (PM_KISAN DISTRICT_ROLLUP — Villupuram)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Found",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"aaaaaaaa-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\n    \"date\": \"2024-11-19\",\n    \"detector_type\": \"NO_SPIKE\",\n    \"scheme_id\": \"PDS\",\n    \"severity\": \"CRITICAL\",\n    \"ai_classification\": \"SUPPLY_FAILURE\",\n    \"ai_confidence\": \"0.910\",\n    \"ai_reasoning\": \"NO% spiked to 78% vs 7-day baseline of 31% — z-score 4.2 indicates a non-random event.\",\n    \"ai_action\": \"Conduct immediate field visit to FPS store at 605001.\",\n    \"ai_action_ta\": \"605001 இல் உள்ள FPS கடைக்கு உடனடி கள வருகை மேற்கொள்ளவும்.\",\n    \"ai_urgency\": \"TODAY\",\n    \"ai_processed_at\": \"2024-11-19T08:59:50.000Z\",\n    \"status\": \"ASSIGNED\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 Not Found",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": \"Anomaly not found\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get AI Processing Stats",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Engine-Secret", "value": "{{engine_secret}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
