              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "anomaly", "stats"]
            },
            "description": "Returns a 7-day summary of anomaly classification counts broken down by type, plus OpenAI API usage and cost metrics.\n\nUseful for dashboard monitoring and cost tracking."
          },
          "response": [
